thfull-its-a-great-loss-3833752">杰米·李·柯蒂斯（Jamie Lee Curtis）向玛丽安·菲斯特尔（Marianne Faithfull）致敬：“这是巨大的损失”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jamie-Lee-Curtis-and-Marianne-Faithfull.-CREDIT_-Steve-Granitz_FilmMagic-and-Frank-Hoensch_Getty-Images-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jamie-Lee-Curtis-and-Marianne-Faithfull.-CREDIT_-Steve-Granitz_FilmMagic-and-Frank-Hoensch_Getty-Images-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jamie-Lee-Curtis-and-Marianne-Faithfull.-CREDIT_-Steve-Granitz_FilmMagic-and-Frank-Hoensch_Getty-Images-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jamie-Lee-Curtis-and-Marianne-Faithfull.-CREDIT_-Steve-Granitz_FilmMagic-and-Frank-Hoensch_Getty-Images-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jamie-Lee-Curtis-and-Marianne-Faithfull.-CREDIT_-Steve-Granitz_FilmMagic-and-Frank-Hoensch_Getty-Images-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jamie-Lee-Curtis-and-Marianne-Faithfull.-CREDIT_-Steve-Granitz_FilmMagic-and-Frank-Hoensch_Getty-Images-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jamie-Lee-Curtis-and-Marianne-Faithfull.-CREDIT_-Steve-Granitz_FilmMagic-and-Frank-Hoensch_Getty-Images-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jamie-lee-curtis">杰米·李·柯蒂斯（Jamie Lee Curtis）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tributes-paid-as-icon-marianne-faithfull-dies-age-78-she-will-be-dearly-missed-3833293">在78岁去世</a>后向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marianne-faithfull">玛丽安·菲斯特尔（Marianne Faithfull）</a>致敬。</p><p>周四（1月30日），这位标志性歌手和演员代表宣布，她“今天在伦敦与她充满爱心的家人的陪伴下和平过世。她会非常想念。”</p><p>自从宣布这一消息以来，来自娱乐界的贡品一直在涌入。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mick-jagger">米克·贾格（Mick Jagger）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mick-jagger-shares-tribute-to-marianne-faithfull-she-was-so-much-part-of-my-life-for-so-long-3833340">向他的前伴侣分享了一个个人信息</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">Metallica</a>则将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/metallica-honour-fearless-marianne-faithfull-3833553">她描述为“无所畏惧”</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-pays-tribute-to-marianne-faithfull-she-brought-us-all-closer-3833606">莫里西（Morrissey）说她“使我们更加接近我们”</a> 。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-mccartney-shares-tribute-to-beautiful-sweet-marianne-faithfull-3833694">保罗·麦卡特尼爵士（Paul McCartney）爵士也分享了一个致敬</a>，称信徒为“美丽而甜蜜”。</p><p>现在，柯蒂斯分享了她对已故艺术家的记忆。柯蒂斯（Curtis）于周五（1月31日）前往Instagram，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/sinead-oconnor-obituary-3473864">2023年去世的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">Sinead O&#39;Connor</a>分享了一张忠实的照片。</p><p>柯蒂斯写道：“这是我第二次发布这张照片。” “第一个是Sinead去世的那一天。我从来没有印刷它，因为玛丽安（Marianne）的眼睛闭上了，但是当Sinead死亡时，我找到了联系表并拍照。由于火灾，我现在无法访问我的照片文件，我刚刚听说玛丽安今天去世了。</p><p>她继续说：“她是我朋友约翰·布尔曼（John Boorman）的好朋友，是一位迷人的艺术家和女人，这是一个巨大的损失。” “当我可以访问我的照片文件时，我会找到更好的照片。我们去了乡村都柏林的一个音乐节，听听阿姆，这对我来说是一个宝贵的回忆。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFdvnOaShZu/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 1